name: Mulan Jameela
description: '''Mulan Jameela''' (born '''Raden Wulansari''' on 23 August 1979) is an Indonesian singer and politician. In 2019, she became a member of the [[People's Representative Council]] ([[Indonesian language|Indonesian]]: ''Dewan Perwakilan Rakyat'', DPR) from the [[Great Indonesia Movement Party|Gerindra Party]], representing [[West Java]].
